    "Horizontal flip, multiplicative noise, and random rotation) for both images the original and the newly reconstructed one.",
    "At the detection phase, one more augmentation technique (mosaic) was used and selected based on previous experiments by [65], as it showed better performance in detection than other techniques that are used with YOLO.",
